### Fetch all teams in the league
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/league
Accept: application/json

### Fetch a specific team by ID
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY
Accept: application/json

### Fetch team - not found
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/INVALID
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — paste the id of a newly created (unassigned) player
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY/paste-created-player-id-here
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — 409 (seed player already on a team)
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY/330eb324-3382-4fca-b20e-2b4c7e278047
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — 404 (team not found)
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/INVALID/330eb324-3382-4fca-b20e-2b4c7e278047
Accept: application/json

### Fetch team roster with lineup slots
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/BOS/roster
Accept: application/json

### Fetch roster — 404 (team not found)
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/INVALID/roster
Accept: application/json

### Set lineup (replace-all; exactly 5 STARTER) — paste this team's real player ids
# Fetch /roster first to get player ids. Every roster player should appear here.
PUT http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/BOS/lineup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "entries": [
    { "playerId": "starter-1-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 1 },
    { "playerId": "starter-2-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 2 },
    { "playerId": "starter-3-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 3 },
    { "playerId": "starter-4-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 4 },
    { "playerId": "starter-5-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 5 },
    { "playerId": "bench-1-id",   "lineupRole": "BENCH" }
  ]
}

### Set lineup — 400 (not exactly 5 starters)
PUT http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/BOS/lineup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "entries": [
    { "playerId": "starter-1-id", "lineupRole": "STARTER", "rotationOrder": 1 }
  ]
}

### Release player from team (to free agency) — paste an id currently on the team
DELETE http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/UT/paste-player-id-on-this-team
Accept: application/json

### Release player — 404 (player not on this team)
DELETE http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/UT/does-not-exist
Accept: application/json
